{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/comicsphere-2018-pasar-komik-unik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Comicsphere 2018 Sajikan Konsep Pasar Komik Nan Unik","content":"<p>Awal bulan Desember 2018 lalu diawali dengan <em>event</em> Comicsphere 2018. Sebagai event komik penutup tahun 2018, pasar komik yang diadakan tanggal 1 Desember lalu diadakan dengan cukup sederhana namun terasa unik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52113\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52113\" data-attachment-id=\"52113\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comicsphere-2018-pasar-komik-unik/attachment/01-comicsphere-2018-report/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-comicsphere-2018-report\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-comicsphere-2018-report-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52113\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" alt=\"Suasana Comicsphere 2018. Sumber CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-comicsphere-2018-report-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52113\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Suasana Comicsphere 2018. Sumber CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Comicsphere 2018 diselenggarakan di Spasial Bandung, sebuah gudang di kompleks tentara TNI yang disulap oleh sekelompok anak muda menjadi salah satu tempat nongkrong <em>hip</em> di kota kembang. Kawula muda Bandung menjadikan Spasial sebagai tempat berekspresi lewat beragam sajian kuliner dan <em>clothing</em>. Ada pula area terbuka yang biasa dijadikan tempat manggung musisi beken skala <em>indie</em> hingga nasional; mulai dari <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/chit-chat-ikkubaru-dhira-bongs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ikkubaru</a> hingga Jamie Aditya.</p>\n<p>Di lokasi yang sama inilah Comicsphere 2018 diadakan. 35 peserta yang terdiri dari <em>circle</em> kreatif hingga komunitas UKM kampus berpartisipasi dalam event perdana ciptaan UKM Balon Kata dari Telkom University. Setelah acara dibuka pukul 9 pagi, aktivitas jual beli komik dan <em>art</em> orisinal pun berlangsung ramai.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/9-circle-comicsphere-booth/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">9 Circle Comicsphere Yang Harus Kamu Datengin Boothnya</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52114\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52114\" data-attachment-id=\"52114\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comicsphere-2018-pasar-komik-unik/attachment/02-comicsphere-2018-report/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-comicsphere-2018-report\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-comicsphere-2018-report-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52114\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" alt=\"Author dan pengunjung saling bercengkerama. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-comicsphere-2018-report-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52114\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Author dan pengunjung saling bercengkerama. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Meskipun diadakan di lokasi yang tergolong kecil, mengeksplor area acara Comicsphere terasa sangat menyenangkan. Para pengunjung menikmati suasana pasar kreatif yang dinamis dan sangat hip lewat estetika lokasi yang sangat <em>cozy</em>, ditambah dengan musik <em>lounge</em> dan <em>smooth jazz </em>yang mengiringi aktivitas belanja atau mengobrol dengan teman. Jika lapar pun, pengunjung bisa mampir sebentar ke café yang masih satu area dengan <em>event</em> Comicsphere 2018 untuk menyantap nasi goreng atau <em>thai tea</em>.</p>\n<p>Di Comicsphere 2018, kreator amatir dan profesional melebur jadi satu. Kapan lagi bisa melihat <em>author</em> amatir dari kampus duduk bersebelahan dengan komikus profesional yang sudah malang melintang di berbagai <em>platform</em> komik? Posisi para peserta yang saling berdekatan menciptakan suasana yang sangat intim dan mendorong adanya kolaborasi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52115\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52115\" data-attachment-id=\"52115\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comicsphere-2018-pasar-komik-unik/attachment/03-comicsphere-2018-report/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-comicsphere-2018-report\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-comicsphere-2018-report-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52115\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg\" alt=\"Sesi talkshow bersama author HeartXBreak, circle Kroma. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-comicsphere-2018-report.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-comicsphere-2018-report-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52115\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sesi talkshow bersama author HeartXBreak, circle Kroma. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Tak hanya berjualan, para kreator pun berkesempatan untuk mempromosikan diri lewat sesi <em>talkshow</em>. Kreator seperti <em>circle</em> Kroma dan wibuverse mendapat kesempatan untuk <em>sharing</em> soal dinamika industri kreatif dan dunia perkomikan. MC juga senantiasa berkeliling area acara dan melakukan tanya jawab dengan para peserta.</p>\n<p>Meski baru acara perdana, Comicsphere 2018 merupakan sebuah <em>event</em> pasar komik yang sangat menjanjikan. Fakta yang cukup mengesankan jika menimbang ini kali pertamanya Balon Kata membuat acara pasar komik yang sukses terlaksana tanpa adanya masalah yang genting. Semoga di tahun 2019 nanti Balon Kata kembali mengadakan Comicsphere yang lebih oke dan lebih meriah.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-attachment-id=\"50176\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-terpopuler-di-indonesia-pada-2018/attachment/print-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1534766427&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Print&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Banner Halaman CIAYO Comics id\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-50176\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" alt=\"Baca komik online di CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"ebf9c97c-cf81-5635-8e80-b377efd12753"}}}